  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>United Streamlands</strong> has to fight the terrible <strong>Frowners</strong> once again, who already occupied and exploited their lands in the past. As <strong>Chief Colonel Pavelson</strong> of the 4th Division \"Black\", you will suddenly find yourself having to defend the independence of your <strong>Country</strong>. <br> <br><strong>Streamlands: Defense</strong> is a Tower Defense with accurate resource management, essential for positioning troops and unlocking upgrades. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/2e598a826efc8d8000f6c7a12c173626.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/2e598a826efc8d8000f6c7a12c173626.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the story in <strong>5 unique Scenarios</strong> with all different mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/278588cc451ca25469d2a0aa9aad19b5.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/278588cc451ca25469d2a0aa9aad19b5.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Read the <strong>documents</strong> to learn about the <strong>history</strong> of this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/490c6bc89a4261aaa0b02e5262e238c5.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/490c6bc89a4261aaa0b02e5262e238c5.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>United Streamlands</strong> has to fight the terrible <strong>Frowners</strong> once again, who already occupied and exploited their lands in the past. As <strong>Chief Colonel Pavelson</strong> of the 4th Division \"Black\", you will suddenly find yourself having to defend the independence of your <strong>Country</strong>. <br> <br><strong>Streamlands: Defense</strong> is a Tower Defense with accurate resource management, essential for positioning troops and unlocking upgrades. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/2e598a826efc8d8000f6c7a12c173626.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/2e598a826efc8d8000f6c7a12c173626.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the story in <strong>5 unique Scenarios</strong> with all different mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/278588cc451ca25469d2a0aa9aad19b5.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/278588cc451ca25469d2a0aa9aad19b5.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Read the <strong>documents</strong> to learn about the <strong>history</strong> of this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras/490c6bc89a4261aaa0b02e5262e238c5.avif?t=1749634186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465180/extras_big/490c6bc89a4261aaa0b02e5262e238c5.avif?t=1749634186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
